{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><p id=\"u6ec04f75\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p><p id=\"u50dde562\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"EWXjA\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入表格卡片</span></h2><p id=\"u19033ccd\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过左上角的卡片统一入口，可以选择「表格」卡片快速插入一个表跟到文档中。</span></p><p id=\"u58770003\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634180783006-580d16d3-a89b-4e4e-8086-bb1db7a57c62.png\" width=\"257.3333333333333\" id=\"u5b6592c6\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ue1a7b0f7\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ue8993fc3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">同时支持以下快捷键（支持中文，拼音及缩写和英文别名）</span></p><p id=\"u57802a31\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/bg</span></code><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/表格</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/biaoge</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/table</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> </span></p><p id=\"u7d3380bf\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649670448026-c9fc9869-2250-49fd-872e-9bae8e7e6340.png\" width=\"775\" id=\"uc06e5352\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u42bfcf93\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"fmgw2\"><span class=\"ne-text\">调整列宽</span></h2><p id=\"u8d75ac4e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">默认表格的列宽是相等的。可通过拖拽改变列宽。</span></p><p id=\"u78b34bbe\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649730504929-2fe4f68b-f159-414a-8a13-c56c50094ae1.png\" width=\"473\" id=\"u1d8fb668\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u35b09ba4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">手动调整过列宽后，悬浮在表格卡片顶部，点击「列等宽」，可在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">表格总宽度不变</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的情况下，快速将现有的列设置为等宽。</span></p><p id=\"u121fe889\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649730793449-3c100ab8-9f8a-4fd2-a845-4625f460c4e8.png\" width=\"740\" id=\"u342a053e\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u2f64e6e2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当前列是等宽的状态下，不会出现「列等宽」的选项。</span></p><p id=\"ub8bf04d3\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649730750708-7df9ed4e-2a1a-4760-92b6-04dc07b3c954.png\" width=\"610\" id=\"uaf34020f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ucb9db722\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"lIaMV\"><span class=\"ne-text\">增删改行列</span></h2><p id=\"u9b410bb8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可通过悬浮在表格的左侧和上侧，快速增删整行/整列。</span></p><p id=\"u1bbac808\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在单元格内的右键面板，也支持更精细的行列单元格操作。</span></p><p id=\"u667e570e\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649732530455-10ade113-3241-42c1-a77e-8ef389f2af8f.png\" width=\"1562\" id=\"u5c5a588b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uda417465\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"jBJXw\"><span class=\"ne-text\">合并单元格</span></h2><p id=\"u02c3fc39\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在表格中选中多个单元格时，可通过顶部工具栏、右键面板或者悬浮工具栏，进行合并单元格的操作。</span></p><p id=\"udbc69f60\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">快捷键是 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Command/Ctrl Shift 1</span></code></p><p id=\"u340156b1\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649729624197-c2d93227-f706-4dad-b48e-039ac99303b9.png\" width=\"746\" id=\"ue3c87b0a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u8d09cb9b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"FaB4T\"><span class=\"ne-text\">调整表格宽度</span></h2><p id=\"u80f02acb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">新建的表格，默认创建为与正文区域等宽的宽度。</span></p><p id=\"uf56dd07c\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649731371496-057c4214-fc70-49c8-80df-4cb34d1e110b.png\" width=\"1448\" id=\"u82819da7\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u583dd507\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">继续新建列或增加列的宽度，即可看到表格宽度变宽，超出正文宽度。</span></p><p id=\"u18e2dfe2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655362275909-f15a4b99-49ad-4525-bc19-8075e3c9944c.png\" width=\"1054\" id=\"ud0a9e04d\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u2a6ede0e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果你希望表格内容与正文一致的宽度，在编辑态点击表格顶部悬浮工具栏的「标宽显示」，可缩短整个表格的宽度。</span></p><p id=\"ue091afcd\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649670356269-f77d52a2-1eea-4a59-8851-2521bc7ef19a.png\" width=\"977\" id=\"u4548ad3a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"yMsAt\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置和正文等宽的表格</span></h3><div data-type=\"color1\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u697f3b30\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Tips：如果先将表格宽度设置为「标宽展示」，标宽下点击「列等宽」，会将</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">表格保持在正文区域的标准宽度</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">且列宽相等。</span></p></div><p id=\"u8b979724\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655362436389-e674134f-c1d2-4dab-bafe-ede98017bec5.png\" width=\"867\" id=\"LrQUd\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u9d4a5ee7\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649730976011-d772379f-62fb-4e3e-aa91-c95b7e774bea.png\" width=\"1522\" id=\"ZjyBZ\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649731007724-eec562b9-40c7-47a4-be35-91dd3b0ea163.png\" width=\"764\" id=\"ArLUs\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uc3d098cf\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"g4fds\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持的格式</span></h2><table id=\"og52w\" class=\"ne-table no-border\" style=\"width: 822px\"><tbody><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"125\"><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u29d77937\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">表格样式</span></p></div></td><td width=\"697\"><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"ub08f229a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持正文的富文本格式，如任务列表、无序列表、有序列表、缩进等，格式快捷键同样适用。</span></p></div></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"125\"><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u9ddec202\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">单元格样式</span></p></div></td><td width=\"697\"><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u04c33400\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">单元格内支持水平和垂直对齐方式。支持隐藏边框。单元格支持设置颜色。</span></p></div></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"125\"><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u2ae89ab6\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">单元格卡片</span></p></div></td><td width=\"697\"><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u7a37e053\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持斜杠或右键插入卡片</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。如图片、状态、语雀内容、附件、代码块等。</span></p></div></td></tr></tbody></table><p id=\"ud82906f8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649733244209-3f848d8a-27ab-4030-b2ad-f5167070e130.png\" width=\"264\" id=\"BVfF8\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649733614703-c073f725-1182-4442-8031-065976d56f23.png\" width=\"131\" id=\"u115d136e\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ua6a7bce3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"sjvWm\"><span class=\"ne-text\">全屏编辑</span></h2><p id=\"ue49da90e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果你有非常多的数据需要编辑，可通过将光标悬浮在表格卡片上，点击悬浮工具栏的「全屏」按钮，进入全屏编辑模式沉浸式编辑。</span></p><p id=\"u658376a7\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634180946833-81ef102f-ffdb-4335-a6f4-32b1b615eaed.png\" width=\"1622\" id=\"u5f2cacfb\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"udbbb953c\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649730015298-9896b933-80db-4fad-9b15-9abd6c3a3584.png\" width=\"992\" id=\"ue5603d30\" class=\"ne-image\"></p></div>",
  "slug": 13900838,
  "title": "如何插入表格"
}